The paper discusses the classification, characteristics, and evaluation of NoSQL databases in the context of big data analytics. This topic falls under several sub-categories of computer science, including database systems (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), distributed and parallel computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and software engineering (cs.SE).
